data.description: Don't miss this beautiful 2 story home in the Twin Eagles neighborhood of Granger. Featuring Primary suite with private bath, 3 additional spacious bedrooms laundry room on the 2nd floor. 12x25 partially covered deck, hard surface flooring on the main level, mudroom, and a fully fenced private yard. The walkout lower level has an additional completed bathroom and is ready for your finishing touches. Extra parking pad and driveway allow for ample parking. All appliances stay. Don't miss this fantastic opportunity to call this place your own!  All information obtained from seller and public records.
